data.description: Over a half acre lot with NO HOA!! And five bedrooms under $300k?!? Bring the whole gang to this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with an open floor plan and situated on a .54 acre corner lot. Built in 2019, this meticulously maintained residence is ready for a new owner. Full suite on the main level, but would be a great office or playroom. Dining area overlooks the kitchen with granite countertops. Great room is anchored by a cozy propane fireplace. Upstairs, you're greeted by a large loft, ideal for a second living area. The primary suite is a true retreat with vaulted ceilings, his & hers closets, and French doors leading to a luxurious bath equipped with a double sink vanity, separate shower, garden tub, and private water closet. Notable standard features include a music port/charging station, recessed lighting, front and back yard irrigation system, stained cabinets, granite countertops, and architectural shingles. Two-car garage and extra-wide driveway. **This property is eligible for 100% financing through a USDA Rural Development Loan program** Buyer must meet eligibility requirements.
